Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.74,0:22:01.49,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}在小憩之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.07,0:22:09.67,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}走在陌生的世界　我思考著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.98,0:22:14.25,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}真實的明天
